WEBVTT

00:03.190 --> 00:06.107
All I wanna know is where are my children.

00:08.206 --> 00:09.524
Four have survived.

00:12.743 --> 00:15.284
All exhibit unique physical conditions.

00:17.877 --> 00:19.599
I just wanna fix my friends.

00:19.917 --> 00:20.954
You can't fix this.

00:23.325 --> 00:25.114
We should use these powers to help people.

00:27.743 --> 00:30.415
You opened a door you don't know how to close.

00:32.269 --> 00:33.995
You don't know anything about what's coming.

00:36.711 --> 00:37.643
What is coming?

00:39.977 --> 00:40.487
Doom.

00:47.113 --> 00:48.556
If you want to stop him,...

00:50.809 --> 00:52.636
...it's gonna take everything you have.

